cat << EOF
Gnonlin is a set of GStreamer elements to ease the creation of non-linear
multimedia editors. It works with the GStreamer multimedia framework to
give developers a powerfull and flexible set of tools for quickly assembling
applications which needs to handle non-linear multimedia editing.
